      <title>Hexo+GitHub搭建博客</title>
      <link href="/2014/03/05/Hexo+GitHub%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
      <url>/2014/03/05/Hexo+GitHub%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3><span id="前言">前言</span></h3><p>写这篇文章纪念下搭建博客遇到的<strong>坑</strong>，以及记录一下怎么快速简便搭建个人博客或者网站</p><h3><span id="关于hexo">关于<strong>hexo</strong></span></h3><p>  <strong>hexo</strong>是一款基于<em>Node.js</em>的静态博客框架，官网地址：<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">前往hexo官网</a></p><h4><span id="hexo的安装和使用"><strong>hexo</strong>的安装和使用</span></h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"My New Post"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Writing</a></p><h4><span id="run-server">Run server</span></h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Server</a></p><h4><span id="generate-static-files">Generate static files</span></h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Generating</a></p><h4><span id="deploy-to-remote-sites">Deploy to remote sites</span></h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
